Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:33.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:49.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.51,0:00:50.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:54.88,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.35,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:01:03.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:10.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:20.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:26.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:33.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:40.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:48.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:53.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:14.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister! Guess what? Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, now I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Belldandy, we should be\nleaving soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:22.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:27.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Skuld. I've got to\ngo to college now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:29.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:45.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:05.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait! No way am I going\nto be defeated by that Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:08.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure Big Sister has\neyes for no one but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:14.98,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! A Heart Stolen by a Goddess?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:28.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm finished building this, I just\nknow it will make Big Sister happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And if that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:36.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the most important\nperson in my life after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:02.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal, being forced to\norganize all the professor's data...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:06.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but on this machine,\nit's taking way too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more push, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His steel body is expanding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get on your feet!{\i0}\NThis gets me pumped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Z! Let's go!{\i0}\NExpanding with one injection!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:22.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, Big Z! You're at Unit 5!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One more shot! One more shot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:30.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An all-purpose robot who will protect\nand serve Big Sister with its devotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:35.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With this on our side, we have\nnothing to fear from Marller either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that's all she wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I guess I should hit Save...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:47.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alternate power source on!\NVoltage is normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Start data read!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, you got him! Finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gyro on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:57.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now releasing the final safety device.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Voltage, okay! Oil pressure, normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All 15 hours and 22 minutes\nof my hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:23.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just when Big Z was about\nto wreak total havoc...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only one person could've done this...\nit's that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do\nabout all that data?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your timing is perfect, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just activated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:41.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the multi-functional Big Sister\NHelper Robot, which I invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:46.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He handles all household chores\nand has a demon-thwarting function.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:49.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's an all-purpose robot\nand his name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei RX!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you made\nanother useless piece of junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:11.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe my data\nwas lost because of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:15.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I missed the part where Big Z\ngoes on a rampage because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna make up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:24.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,15 hours and 22 minutes worth of work\nwent down the drain for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:31.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This robot I built...\nhe really is useful, he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:36.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, sorry. I was too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:41.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You watch, he's incredible!\NBanpei is absolutely incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're such a crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}PROTECT THE TARGET\NSET/COMPLETED{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! Activation successful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that, a new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:09.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing but a piece\nof junk that Skuld created.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:19.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me! You're not a\npiece of junk, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:32.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you, Mr. Banpei!\nI'd like to be your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:40.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My, are you going to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:08:00.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! They totally underestimated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No sign of vigilance whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:08.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Little do they know what a terrible plan\nI have up my sleeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:14.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll force that Keiichi to take this\nmaximum strength hair-growth potion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:18.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I bought through the mail. Belldandy\nwill be disgusted with hairy Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:22.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and she'll be sure to leave Earth then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:26.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, should I go with the potion\nthat will make his skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:29.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...turn green and keep growing like\ncrazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it's better to use this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:38.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good to do\nthe laundry on a sunny day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:42.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at that blue sky\nand those white clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it makes me feel so much\nat peace with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:49.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it's so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:58.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided! I'll use this potion that\nwill make his feet itch for 30 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ATTACK MODE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ATTACK MODE\NDEMON/AUTOMATIC{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marller!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was Marller here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:41.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:45.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And we were saved by this little fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see? He's useful, just like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:51.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:53.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:54.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, well done indeed. So...{\i0}\NThank you, Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:57.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, well done indeed. So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please turn it off as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:03.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,''The Galaxy Vagabond Force''\nis about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:12.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we just got rid of Marller.\NWhy do I have to get yelled at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:17.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it doesn't matter,\nsince I made Big Sister happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:26.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now I'm set to\nre-organize all that data...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:30.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Deromasa Hankachou at two\nis an absolute must-see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:36.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for guarding the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:42.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}STANDBY MODE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:46.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, is he powered down?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:49.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for him for\nnot being able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:53.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was this the switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My data's gone again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:01.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Deromasa's love scene!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:05.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop powering on that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:08.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it's you,\nI won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The next time it happens, I'll trash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:14.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind activating it\nwhile we're at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:15.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Banpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have a purpose in life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:31.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were\nbrought into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in this world\nis born out of necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you have nothing to\nworry about. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Skuld?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try to\ninsert a booster circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:02.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it works, he'll be able to operate\non half the amount of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:08.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure that Banpei will\nappreciate how much you care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:12.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:19.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm the one who built Banpei, I want\nyou to let me finish the job on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:25.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let me bring you\nthe ice cream I made yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:38.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The lights didn't go out, either!\NWe did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:42.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is the power gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:50.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the big idea, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:55.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ATTACK MODE\NNORMAL{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:12.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:30.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...\nhe's got a power cord...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:34.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's not programmed to attack people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:39.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That might be true, but he sure\nwasn't trying to be friends just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:42.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}\nI wonder what happened to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:46.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The data's been rewritten to\nmake him protect Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...from anyone who gets near her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:55.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,According to the log, he used the booster\ncircuit to rewrite the data himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:04.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure there must\nbe some kind of reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:08.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We might be able to pinpoint the\nreason if we power him on again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ATTACK MODE\NNORMAL{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, will he be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:24.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sure he'll figure\nit out somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AUDIO: REPLAY\NThank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:45.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AUDIO: REPLAY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AUDIO: REPLAY\NThank you...thank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:10.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. You know that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:13.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Skuld is the person\nwho created you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:18.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld, Keiichi, and Urd\nare all important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So please, try to get along with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}MEMORY\NSAVE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:27.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, can you believe it?\NThat's MY Big Sister he stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:31.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something about it?\NYou made it yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:34.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do what about it, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you brought us some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:53.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After monopolizing\NMY Big Sister all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to try harder to fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:04.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's starting to warm up to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, there's no way!{\i0}\NMaybe he's starting to warm up to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:10.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he just won't leave\NBelldandy's side, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:16.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, it's so obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:26.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one conclusion\nI never wanted to utter myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:29.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah no, there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:32.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:40.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I never installed\nany emotion circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:44.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy has something inside her\nthat no one will ever understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:51.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a power that draws everyone to her,\nwhether human or object.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:03.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You pour your soul into making lunch\nfor those who are dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:07.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll be modified someday\nso that you can eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:21.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:32.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spike your lunch with this potion, and\na beanstalk will grow from your nostrils!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:39.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You moron. As if I'd fall for\nthe same tactic over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marller!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:54.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's my Big Sister's\nlunch box! You give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! What chance does a child have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:01.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't you dare\ntreat me like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You old nag demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:03.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you say?{\i0}\NYou old nag demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:08.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to go that far,\nI think I'll take you on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! That the best you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not that meddlesome thing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:28.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three minutes and\nyou still haven't answered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:33.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're taking a little nap now,\nsince it's so nice out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:37.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can understand that!\NThis is the perfect day to take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:40.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, there's some kind of\ncommotion going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:58.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to get the best of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Listen, you, stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:32.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei, just do exactly as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:40.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd fall for the same trick again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:06.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The lunch box!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:14.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister's precious lunch box!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:37.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:39.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's the cable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:45.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! His memory's going to get erased!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:48.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei! Banpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}MEMORY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}MEMORY\nIMPORTANT{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:54.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}LUNCH BOX{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}LUNCH BOX\NSKULD{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}PURPOSE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:09.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this have to happen? Banpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:10.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei! Banpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:13.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Skuld? What happened?{\i0}\NBanpei! Banpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:16.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei! Banpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:23.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld did her best to\nrestore Banpei's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:26.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it was too late.\NBanpei's memory was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:28.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:29.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:34.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, both Skuld and\NBelldandy seem to believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:40.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...somewhere deep down, a fragment of\NBanpei's memory lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:49.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}MEMORY\NTHANK YOU{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:56.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and your\NDreams. You have a Wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:02.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much it hurts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it hurts me that\nI can't tell you how I feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:12.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and I have matching hearts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:17.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we must share the\nsame scars deep down inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:23.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now that I'm in your arms,\nI think I can catch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:28.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...your pounding heartbeat this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:33.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody else matters...\NAll we have to do is gaze at each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:39.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right for your heart to flutter...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:44.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:49.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away from happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:55.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be waiting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:24:00.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So come rest your wings anytime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:05.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right to cry...\nanytime you need to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:11.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want to see you again...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:16.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.15,0:24:21.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want you to be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:26.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The demon is enraged, and swears\nto get revenge on the goddesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.59,0:24:29.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And so the demon-god is resurrected,\nand spreads misfortune everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.96,0:24:33.37,AMG next episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, ''Ah! Misfortune Arrives,\nand the Tea-Stalk Stands Upright?''
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.37,0:24:37.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why the Earth Spirit ran,\nand got captured by the little girl?
